Jianbing (煎饼) News Post Machine

Automatically post news of "煎饼" etc. to newsmth.net

Methodology:
(1) Crawl news of "煎饼" from Sogou News search (WAP version), store them.
(2) Pick a new article from the storage, and post it in the board DCST.THU of newsmth.net

Required 3rd-party libraries: beautifulsoup4 (4.2.0), python readability, pymmseg
http://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/bs4/download/4.2/beautifulsoup4-4.2.0.tar.gz
https://github.com/buriy/python-readability

You need to create an "smthdcst.config" to store your username and password for newsmth.net, separated by \t.

